<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About SonicHive — Dubai's Acoustic Pod Pioneers</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{--bg:#FAFAFA;--bg2:#F2F3F5;--bg3:#E8EAED;--red:#D42020;--red-d:rgba(212,32,32,.07);--red-b:rgba(212,32,32,.22);--text:#0A0A0F;--muted:#6B7280;--border:rgba(0,0,0,.09);--card:rgba(0,0,0,.03);--fh:'Poppins',sans-serif;--fb:'Poppins',sans-serif;--max:1280px}
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--fb);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-x:hidden}
    a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
    img{max-width:100%;display:block}
    .wrap{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem}
    .r{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
    .r.on{opacity:1;transform:none}
    .d1{transition-delay:.1s}.d2{transition-delay:.2s}.d3{transition-delay:.3s}.d4{transition-delay:.4s}
    .s-label{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:.9rem}
    .s-title{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin-bottom:1rem}

    /* NAV */
    #nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:1000;background:rgba(250,250,250,.95);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.06)}
    .nav-i{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;padding:1.2rem 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:2rem}
    .logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
    .logo-t{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.02em}
    .logo-t em{color:var(--red);font-style:normal}
    .nav-links{display:flex;gap:1.75rem;align-items:center}
    .nav-links a{font-size:.875rem;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;transition:color .2s}
    .nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.cur{color:var(--text)}
    .nav-cta{background:var(--red);color:#FFFFFF;border:none;border-radius:100px;padding:.6rem 1.4rem;font-size:.875rem;font-weight:400;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--fb)}

    /* HERO */
    .about-hero{padding:9rem 2rem 6rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
    .about-hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%,rgba(212,32,32,.05),transparent 60%)}
    .about-hero::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,var(--red-b),transparent)}
    .ah-inner{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;position:relative}
    .ah-left .s-label{margin-bottom:.9rem}
    .ah-left h1{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:clamp(2.8rem,5.5vw,5rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.04em;line-height:.95;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
    .ah-left h1 em{color:var(--red);font-style:normal}
    .ah-left p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem}
    .ah-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2.5rem}
    .ah-stat{padding:1.25rem;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;text-align:center}
    .ah-stat-n{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:2rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--red);line-height:1}
    .ah-stat-l{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:.35rem;line-height:1.4}
    .ah-right{position:relative}
    .about-img-stack{position:relative;height:460px}
    .aimg-main{position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:85%;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;height:340px}
    .aimg-main img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
    .aimg-accent{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;width:55%;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;height:200px;border:3px solid var(--bg2)}
    .aimg-accent img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
    .aimg-badge{position:absolute;top:1.5rem;left:1.5rem;background:rgba(5,8,15,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border:1px solid var(--red-b);border-radius:12px;padding:.75rem 1rem;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--red)}

    /* MISSION */
    #mission{padding:7rem 0}
    .mission-lay{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6rem;align-items:center}
    .mission-txt .s-label{margin-bottom:.9rem}
    .mission-txt h2{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,2.8rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.05}
    .mission-txt p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.85;font-size:.975rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem}
    .mission-txt blockquote{border-left:2px solid var(--red);padding:.75rem 0 .75rem 1.5rem;margin:2rem 0;font-family:var(--fh);font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--text);line-height:1.4}
    .mission-visual{background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.06);border-radius:24px;padding:2.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2rem}
    .mv-item{display:flex;gap:1.25rem;align-items:flex-start}
    .mv-ic{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:11px;background:var(--red-d);border:1px solid var(--red-b);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:.1rem}
    .mv-item h3{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:.95rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:.35rem}
    .mv-item p{font-size:.875rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65}

    /* CLIENTS */
    #clients{padding:6rem 0;background:var(--bg2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
    .clients-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem}
    .clients-head p{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:.5rem}
    .clients-head h2{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--text)}
    .clients-row{display:flex;gap:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;align-items:center}
    .client-tag{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:.65rem 1.5rem;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.04em;transition:all .2s}
    .client-tag:hover{border-color:var(--red-b);color:var(--text)}

    /* VALUES */
    #values{padding:7rem 0}
    .val-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:4rem}
    .val-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem}
    .val-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:2.5rem;transition:border-color .3s,transform .3s}
    .val-card:hover{border-color:var(--red-b);transform:translateY(-5px)}
    .val-num{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--red);opacity:.25;line-height:1;margin-bottom:1rem}
    .val-name{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:.65rem}
    .val-desc{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7}

    /* JOURNEY TIMELINE */
    #journey{padding:7rem 0;background:var(--bg2)}
    .journey-head{margin-bottom:4rem}
    .timeline{position:relative;padding-left:2rem}
    .timeline::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:8px;bottom:0;width:1px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--red),rgba(232,160,48,.1))}
    .tl-item{position:relative;padding-left:2rem;margin-bottom:3rem}
    .tl-item:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
    .tl-dot{position:absolute;left:-2rem;top:6px;width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);border:2px solid var(--bg2);transform:translateX(-50%)}
    .tl-year{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:.35rem}
    .tl-title{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:.4rem}
    .tl-desc{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65}

    /* CTA */
    #about-cta{padding:7rem 0;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    #about-cta::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%,rgba(212,32,32,.05),transparent 65%)}
    .acta-inner{position:relative;text-align:center;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto}
    .acta-inner h2{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin-bottom:1rem}
    .acta-inner p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-size:1.05rem}
    .btn-row{display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .btn-g{background:var(--red);color:#FFFFFF;border:none;border-radius:100px;padding:.875rem 2.25rem;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:400;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;font-family:var(--fb);display:inline-block}
    .btn-g:hover{transform:scale(1.04);box-shadow:0 0 28px rgba(232,160,48,.45)}
    .btn-o{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);border-radius:100px;padding:.875rem 2.25rem;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;font-family:var(--fb);display:inline-block}
    .btn-o:hover{border-color:var(--red-b);color:var(--red)}

    /* FOOTER */
    footer{background:#0A0A0A;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:4.5rem 0 2rem}
    .foot-g{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1.3fr;gap:3rem;margin-bottom:3.5rem}
    .foot-brand p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin-top:1rem;max-width:280px}
    .foot-soc{display:flex;gap:.75rem;margin-top:1.5rem}
    .soc-a{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:400;transition:all .2s;color:var(--muted)}
    .soc-a:hover{background:var(--red-d);border-color:var(--red-b);color:var(--red)}
    .foot-col h4{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:.8rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1.25rem}
    .foot-col a{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:.875rem;margin-bottom:.6rem;transition:color .2s}
    .foot-col a:hover{color:var(--text)}
    .foot-contact p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.875rem;margin-bottom:.6rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.45rem}
    .foot-contact a{color:var(--red);display:inline;margin-bottom:0}
    .foot-bot{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:2rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem}
    .foot-bot p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.8rem}
    .foot-locs{display:flex;gap:.6rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .foot-locs span{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted);background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:100px;padding:.2rem .7rem}

    @media(max-width:1024px){.ah-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:3rem}.mission-lay{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:3rem}.val-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.foot-g{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
    @media(max-width:768px){.val-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.foot-g{grid-template-columns:1fr}.ah-stats{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.about-img-stack{height:280px}.aimg-main{height:240px}.aimg-accent{height:140px}}
    /* MEGA MENU */
    .nav-dd{position:static;display:flex;align-items:center}
    .nd-toggle{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted);font-size:.875rem;font-weight:500;border:none;background:none;font-family:var(--fb);padding:0;transition:color .2s;position:relative;padding-bottom:2px}
    .nav-dd.open .nd-toggle,.nd-toggle:hover{color:var(--text)}
    .nd-chev{transition:transform .25s ease;flex-shrink:0}
    .nav-dd.open .nd-chev{transform:rotate(180deg)}
    .mega-wrap{position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 14px);left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(-12px);width:min(1080px,calc(100vw - 2rem));background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.09);border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.04),0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.1);opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .22s ease,transform .22s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);z-index:400}
    .nav-dd.open .mega-wrap{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}
    .mega-wrap::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:15%;right:15%;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(212,32,32,.8) 40%,rgba(212,32,32,.9) 50%,rgba(212,32,32,.8) 60%,transparent);z-index:2}
    .mega-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:transparent}
    .mega-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:1.1rem 1.5rem .85rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .mega-eye{font-size:.6rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35)}
    .mega-all-link{font-size:.76rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.4);transition:color .2s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.35rem}
    .mega-all-link:hover{color:rgba(0,0,0,.8)}
    .mega-divider{height:1px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
    .mega-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:.4rem;padding:1rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .mc{display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem 1.4rem;border-radius:14px;text-decoration:none;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:background .2s}
    .mc::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid transparent;transition:border-color .2s;pointer-events:none}
    .mc-img-w{height:160px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:.9rem}
    .mc-img-w img{height:150px;width:auto;object-fit:contain;filter:drop-shadow(0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.2));transition:transform .35s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1),filter .35s ease}
    .mc:hover .mc-img-w img{transform:translateY(-8px) scale(1.06);filter:drop-shadow(0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.28))}
    .mc-svg-w{height:120px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:.9rem;transition:transform .35s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1)}
    .mc:hover .mc-svg-w{transform:translateY(-6px) scale(1.05)}
    .mc-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:.59rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.17rem .65rem;border-radius:100px;margin-bottom:.45rem;width:fit-content}
    .mc-name{font-size:.95rem;font-weight:400;color:#0A0A0F;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:.3rem}
    .mc-desc{font-size:.71rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.45);line-height:1.55;flex:1}
    .mc-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;margin-top:.7rem;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:400;opacity:0;transform:translateX(-5px);transition:opacity .18s,transform .18s}
    .mc:hover .mc-link{opacity:1;transform:none}
    .mc-vrt:hover{background:rgba(212,32,32,.05)}.mc-vrt:hover::after{border-color:rgba(212,32,32,.2)}.mc-vrt .mc-badge{background:rgba(212,32,32,.1);color:#EF5050;border:1px solid rgba(212,32,32,.22)}.mc-vrt .mc-link{color:#EF5050}
    .mc-plus:hover{background:rgba(184,134,11,.05)}.mc-plus:hover::after{border-color:rgba(146,64,14,.22)}.mc-plus .mc-badge{background:rgba(184,134,11,.1);color:#92400E;border:1px solid rgba(146,64,14,.25)}.mc-plus .mc-link{color:#92400E}
    .mc-art:hover{background:rgba(99,102,241,.05)}.mc-art:hover::after{border-color:rgba(67,56,202,.2)}.mc-art .mc-badge{background:rgba(99,102,241,.1);color:#4338CA;border:1px solid rgba(67,56,202,.22)}.mc-art .mc-link{color:#4338CA}
    .mc-home:hover{background:rgba(20,184,166,.05)}.mc-home:hover::after{border-color:rgba(15,118,110,.2)}.mc-home .mc-badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,.1);color:#0F766E;border:1px solid rgba(15,118,110,.22)}.mc-home .mc-link{color:#0F766E}
    .mega-foot{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.25rem;padding:.85rem 1.5rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);position:relative;z-index:1}
    .mf-link{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.45rem;font-size:.76rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.45);transition:color .2s;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap}
    .mf-link:hover{color:rgba(0,0,0,.75)}
    .mf-sep{width:1px;height:14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.1);flex-shrink:0}
    .mf-cta{color:rgba(212,32,32,.75)!important}.mf-cta:hover{color:#D42020!important}
  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){*,*::before,*::after{animation-duration:.01ms!important;transition-duration:.01ms!important;animation-iteration-count:1!important}}
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('../partials/header', { page: 'about' }) %>
<div id="main-content" tabindex="-1" style="outline:none;position:absolute"></div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="ah-inner">
    <div class="ah-left r">
      <p class="s-label">Our Story</p>
      <h1>We Built <em>Silence</em> Into a Product.</h1>
      <p>Born in Dubai. Engineered for the Middle East's most ambitious workspaces. SonicHive set out to solve the one problem that open-plan offices never cracked — giving people a place to think, speak, and meet without the noise of everyone around them.</p>
      <div class="ah-stats">
        <div class="ah-stat"><div class="ah-stat-n">500+</div><div class="ah-stat-l">Pods installed across 5 countries</div></div>
        <div class="ah-stat"><div class="ah-stat-n">100+</div><div class="ah-stat-l">Corporate clients across the region</div></div>
        <div class="ah-stat"><div class="ah-stat-n">30dB</div><div class="ah-stat-l">Industry-leading noise reduction</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ah-right r d2">
      <div class="about-img-stack">
        <div class="aimg-main">
          <img src="https://thesonichive.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/23-10-2024-18_27_04-1024x517.webp" alt="SonicHive office pods in use">
        </div>
        <div class="aimg-accent">
          <img src="https://thesonichive.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Office-pods-for-4-person_Sonichive-2-1024x819.webp" alt="Quartet pod">
        </div>
        <div class="aimg-badge"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" style="width:20px;height:20px"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z"/></svg> Downtown Dubai Showroom</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MISSION -->
<section id="mission">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="mission-lay">
      <div class="mission-txt r">
        <p class="s-label">Our Mission</p>
        <h2>The Noise Problem Deserves a Real Solution.</h2>
        <p>Open-plan offices transformed how people work together — but they created a new problem. With nowhere to focus, nowhere to speak privately, and nowhere to meet without disturbing everyone around you, productivity suffers.</p>
        <p>SonicHive was founded on a simple belief: acoustic privacy shouldn't require permanent construction, massive budgets, or sacrificing your office's design aesthetic. It should be modular, beautiful, and instant.</p>
        <blockquote>"Silence is not the absence of sound. It's the presence of focus."</blockquote>
        <p>With the largest acoustic lab in Asia behind our engineering, and a team based in the heart of Dubai, we bring world-class acoustic science to every pod we build.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-visual r d2">
        <div class="mv-item">
          <div class="mv-ic"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" style="width:20px;height:20px"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 0 1 4.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0 1 12 15a9.065 9.065 0 0 0-6.23-.693L5 14.5m14.8.8 1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0 1 12 21c-2.93 0-5.796-.232-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5"/></svg></div>
          <div><h3>Acoustic Lab Engineering</h3><p>Our pods are developed with backing from the largest acoustic testing lab in Asia — ensuring every model delivers genuine, measurable noise reduction.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mv-item">
